data.description: MOVE IN READY!  Don't miss this freshly remodeled home with that often searched for 4th bedroom! Home has many updates, including an additional heated and cooled 300 sq ft sunroom, not included in sq footage. New roof, large kitchen, extra insulation and privacy fence. Nice storage with pantry and built in shelves. Storage shed in yard could also be converted into a guest room as it's already got flooring, power, and shelving. Large fenced yard with privacy fence divided into 2 sections. Additional parking in the rear. Don't miss out on this one!  Call today!
